title: World ranking of Sweden 's national football team 1993 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes FIFA World Ranking position. In total the number of data points it has is 26.
Overall FIFA World Ranking position has increased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest FIFA World Ranking position, of value 44.0 was reached at Year 2014
The lowest FIFA World Ranking position, of value 3.0 was reported at Year 1994
